gn=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Fear Break Guide</span><hr size=1> Some good ideas there Kellroy, I do have one question though.  Why Lev / SOE in fear?<br>
<br>
Those little impy guys proc something like shadowstep.  Shadowstep is a funny thing, it will ONLY take you down hill.  If the MT is levved he is going to go a LONG ways.  I found from tanking there myself that if I could stand in a small depression that the shadowsteps were mostly very short.  If the mob got pushed up a slope away from my little depression and I had to follow it, then that proc could send me most of the way to the fetid fiend house. Which COULD be problematic. <br>
<br>
As MT I hate these impy guys worse than I hate the dispelling cone looking guys.<br>
<br>
I can see chanters wanting LEV and a TALL illusion if they are gnomes.  I can see some of the non-tank melees wanting lev.  Just don't lev the MT.<br>
<br>
